The inputstream is not thread-safe. 
1) If it is shared by multi-threads, it should be synchronized, so it will be read by only one thread at the same time. Once it is read, the count is -1 or greater than 0;
2) If each thread has its own inputstream, i.e. not shared by other threads, the private inputstream will be read util end of stream reached;

To sum up, as you can see, the scenario that the count is 0 will not happen.
